==English==
===Etymology===
Sometimes claimed to be from Indian vernacular for ''[[fuck]]'', though no confirmation has been found
===Noun===
'''choad'''
#{{slang}} a general [[insult]], referring to someone as a [[loser]], etc.
#{{slang}} [[penis]]
#{{slang}} A person who is short, and fat.
#{{slang}} A penis that is wider, than is long.

*Choad can also mean -> To ejeculate on a woman's face.

